ADO EKITI – The Secretary of the former and serving National ex Officio forum of the People’s Democratic Party(PDP),  Hon Hellen Taiwo-Adebakin has felicitated with the former governor of Osun State, Prince Olagunsoye Oyinlola on the occasion of his birthday. Adebakin in her birthday message described  Prince Oyinlola as a true party man  and one of the pillars of the PDP in Nigeria who had contributed in no small measure to the growth of the party. ” I celebrate with our leader,  father and mentor on the occasion of your birthday anniversary. You are no doubt a shining example and an inspiration to the younger generation. New Year: Adebakin Congratulates Nigerians, Says Help On The Way Hon. Adebakin Hails Silverbird At 20 “You left indelible prints as governor of Osun state and most of  your achievements still remain a reference point to successive administrations  in the state “Your active roles in the ongoing efforts to reposition our party cannot be underestimated. I pray to God Almighty to continue to protect you and give you sound health to be able to celebrate many more years in prosperity. I say happy birthday to you sir ” Adebakin said. End